                    <span>2014-09-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">in pdf</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="732657542">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-732657542" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-732657542" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="732657542">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/suguangen/">落凤坡</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-11-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">典型的树碑立传之作，对其研究的对象缺少足够的距离感，又无多少深入的分析。事实上作者对苏格兰人杰出成就的夸夸其谈，多少反映了他其实并不清楚苏格兰人究竟特殊在哪里</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

